The coupon on Dai-Ichi Hotel Ltd's 50 mlnSwiss franc issue of five-year notes with equity warrants hasbeen cut to 1-5/8 pct from the indicated 1-7/8 pct, leadmanager Swiss Volksbank said.    The warrants have an exercise price of 1,507 yen per share,compared with the last traded price of 1,470 yen, it said.    The notes are guarantees by Long-Term Credit Bank of JapanLtd. Payment is due on March 25. REUTER&#3;